This is an add-on policies for Perl::Critic checking for
miscellaneous bugs, compatibility, efficiency, and cosmetic things.

The only prerequisite is Perl::Critic itself, though the
"PerlMinimumVersionAndWhy" policy does nothing without
Perl::MinimumVersion.

The Perl-Critic-Policy-Plicease-ProhibitArrayAssignAref home page is

    https://github.com/uperl/Perl-Critic-Policy-Plicease-ProhibitArrayAssignAref
